reviewText: It's not as good as "Don't Make Him Angery", but it's still really good! Still the animated character bringing his stories to life. I would buy it again. :)
Title: Jo Koy: Lights Out

reviewText: Sometimes a SON has to just LET IT ALL OUT!!  Which he manages to do in a brutally honest, yet caring and hilarious way!! He'll have you LOL! Does an incredible job of relaying his message so we "feel his pain"! He tells it like he felt it, sharing personal, private stories, including the relationship he has with his MOM! One less star for swearing more than usual in this one. You may not care.The seller sent my purchase right on time and in excellent condition! I recommend this movie, and this seller to buy it from! Have FUN!
Title: Jo Koy: Lights Out

reviewText: I gave this to my granddaughter for Christmas. She made a point of letting me know how much she enjoyed it.
Title: Jo Koy: Lights Out

reviewText: I love Jo Koy and have a couple of his standups on dvd. This particular one still has his great timing style but it just wasn't as funny. My favorite joke he did is the last one on the dvd because I live it every day and night. I think this is better as a rental.
